%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EArchana%20Kamath%20will%20dearly%20miss%20donning%20the%20Indian%20jersey%2C%20but%20the%20table%20tennis%20player%20is%20determined%20to%20serve%20the%20country%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bdifferent%20way%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20future%2C%20helping%20to%20shape%20its%20public%20policies%20as%20an%20economist.%20Days%20after%20recording%20India's%20only%20success%20in%20the%20quarterfinal%20loss%20to%20Germany%20in%20the%20recent%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20the%2024-year-old%20from%20Bengaluru%20has%20re-entered%20student%20life%20in%20the%20USA%20where%20she%20is%20studying%20for%20a%20Master's%20in%20Public%20Policy%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20started%20her%20professional%20career%20as%20a%20teenager%2C%20Archana's%20decision%20to%20move%20away%20from%20table%20tennis%20has%20been%20quite%20emotional.%20But%20she%20has%20equally%20enjoyed%20studying%20since%20her%20school%20days%20where%20she%20was%20a%20topper%2C%20securing%2098.7%20and%2097%20percent%20in%20her%2010th%20and%2012th%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20she%20is%20pursuing%20her%20second%20master's%20degree%20in%20Michigan%2C%20having%20already%20completed%20her%20post-graduation%20in%20International%20Relations.%20Archana%20obtained%20her%20bachelor's%20degree%20in%20economics%20and%20she%20wants%20to%20return%20to%20India%20after%20two%20years%20and%20serve%20the%20nation%2C%20probably%20as%20an%20economist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20role%20models%20range%20from%20well-known%20economist%20Sanjeev%20Sanyal%20to%20the%20likes%20of%20tennis%20stars%20Carlos%20Alcaraz%20and%20Rafael%20Nadal%20whom%20she%20met%20at%20the%20Games%20Village%20in%20Paris%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20PTI%20from%20Ann%20Arbor%20in%20Michigan%2C%20Archana%20explained%20her%20decision%20to%20leave%20elite%20sport%20right%20after%20the%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20categorically%20stated%20that%20%26quot%3Bshe%20is%20not%20in%20it%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20better%20financial%20future%20as%20she%20has%20been%20taken%20care%20of%20by%20her%20employers%20Indian%20Oil%2C%20OGQ%2C%20and%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20always%20liked%20studying%2C%20as%20much%20as%20table%20tennis.%20I%20had%20inquired%20about%20this%20course%20in%20Michigan%20last%20year%20as%20well%20but%20then%20we%20qualified%20for%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20as%20a%20team%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20that%20the%20Olympics%20are%20done%2C%20I%20want%20to%20study%20more%20and%20come%20back%20to%20India%20after%20two%20years%20and%20serve%20the%20people%20in%20a%20different%20capacity.%20My%20decision%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20financial%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20got%20all%20the%20support%20I%20have%20needed%20while%20playing%20for%20India%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20biggest%20honour%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20soft-spoken%20athlete%2C%20who%20has%20gone%20to%20Michigan%20after%20applying%20for%20a%20study%20leave%20with%20her%20employer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20comes%20from%20a%20financially%20secure%20family%20of%20doctors%20with%20both%20her%20parents%20being%20ophthalmologists.%20Her%20brother%20is%20currently%20pursuing%20a%20PHD%20in%20aerospace%20engineering%20in%20the%20USA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20memories%20cannot%20be%20ripped%20away%20from%20table%20tennis%20as%20it%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20both%20Indian%20men%20and%20women%20had%20qualified%20for%20the%20team%20event%20of%20the%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchana%20hopes%20to%20continue%20playing%20table%20tennis%20in%20the%20USA%20and%20will%20miss%20the%20team%20environment%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20best%20thing%20about%20the%20Olympics%20was%20being%20with%20seniors%20like%20Sharath%20Kamal%20and%20Manika%20Batra.%20The%20environment%20was%20so%20good.%20I%20also%20got%20to%20meet%20Novak%20Djokovic%2C%20Rafael%20Nadal%20and%20Carlos%20Alcaraz.%20I%20made%20memories%20for%20life%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20also%20loved%20fighting%20for%20my%20country%20and%20that%20is%20something%20I%20will%20miss%20the%20most.%20I%20hope%20to%20keep%20playing%20here%20(in%20the%20US)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchana%20is%20certain%20about%20being%20a%20public%20servant%20in%20India%20after%20her%20course%20in%20Michigan%20but%20she%20is%20yet%20to%20work%20out%20the%20finer%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20always%20been%20interested%20in%20policy%20making.%20The%20main%20goal%20is%20to%20serve%20India.%20I%20just%20want%20to%20see%20how%20I%20go%20about%20my%20course.%20The%20eventual%20goal%20is%20to%20come%20back%20and%20serve%20India.%26quot%3B%20So%2C%20has%20she%20thought%20deeply%20about%20being%20an%20economist%3F%20%26quot%3BI%20really%20admire%20Sanjeev%20Sanyal's%20work.%20His%20wide%20range%20of%20work%20inspires%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Archana%2C%20who%20began%20attending%20lectures%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724380500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fkksp49n8_archana-kamath-afp_625x300_22_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fnot-money-paris-olympics-star-archana-kamath-reveals-real-reason-behind-quitting-table-tennis-6394468%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Having%20started%20her%20professional%20career%20as%20a%20teenager%2C%20Archana%20Kamath's%20decision%20to%20move%20away%20from%20table%20tennis%20has%20been%20quite%20emotional.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fnot-money-paris-olympics-star-archana-kamath-reveals-real-reason-behind-quitting-table-tennis-6394468%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kalki%3A%20Fans%20laud%20Big%20B%3B%20mi