amol%20300mg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20also%20banned%20the%20combination%20of%20Paracetamol%2C%20Tramadol%2C%20Taurine%20and%20Caffeine.%20Tramadol%20is%20an%20opioid-based%20pain%20killer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Central%20government%20is%20satisfied%20that%20the%20use%20of%20the%20Fixed%20Dose%20Combination%20drug%20is%20likely%20to%20involve%20risk%20to%20human%20beings%20whereas%20safer%20alternatives%20to%20the%20said%20drug%20are%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notification%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%20matter%20was%20examined%20by%20an%20Expert%20Committee%20appointed%20by%20the%20Centre%20which%20considered%20these%20FDCs%20as%20%26quot%3Birrational%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20stated%20that%20the%20apex%20panel%20Drugs%20Technical%20Advisory%20Board%20(DTAB)%20also%20examined%20these%20FDCs%20and%20recommended%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20therapeutic%20justification%20for%20the%20ingredients%20contained%20in%20these%20FDCs%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20FDC%20may%20involve%20risk%20to%20human%20beings.%20Hence%20in%20the%20larger%20public%20interest%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20prohibit%20the%20manufacture%2C%20sale%20or%20distribution%20of%20this%20FDC%20under%20section%2026%20A%20of%20Drugs%20and%20Cosmetics%20Act%201940%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notification%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20above%2C%20any%20kind%20of%20regulation%20or%20restriction%20to%20allow%20for%20any%20use%20in%20patients%20is%20not%20justifiable.%20Therefore%2C%20only%20prohibition%20under%20section%2026A%20is%20recommended%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20DTAB's%20recommendations%2C%20the%20notification%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Central%20government%20is%20satisfied%20that%20it%20is%20necessary%20and%20expedient%20in%20public%20interest%20to%20prohibit%20the%20manufacture%2C%20sale%20and%20distribution%20for%20human%20use%20of%20the%20said%20drug%20in%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20includes%20certain%20products%20which%20were%20already%20discontinued%20by%20many%20drug%20makers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20in%202016%20had%20announced%20the%20ban%20on%20the%20manufacture%2C%20sale%20and%20distribution%20of%20344%20drug%20combinations%20after%20an%20expert%20panel%2C%20set%20up%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20had%20stated%20they%20were%20being%20sold%20to%20patients%20without%20scientific%20data%20and%20the%20order%20was%20challenged%20by%20the%20manufacturers%20in%20court%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202023%2C%2014%20FDCs%20which%20were%20part%20of%20those%20344%20drug%20combinations%2C%20were%20banned.%20Many%20of%20the%20FDCs%20banned%20recently%20were%20also%20from%20those%20344%20drug%20combinations%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724378460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ftib0u67o_medicine-generic_625x300_25_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-bans-156-combination-medicines-used-for-fever-pain-cold-6395411%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20has%20banned%20156%20widely%20sold%20fixed-dose%20combination%20(FDC)%20drugs%20including%20antibacterial%20medicines%20used%20for%20fever%2C%20cold%2C%20allergies%20and%20pain%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Blikely%20to%20involve%20risk%20to%20human%20beings%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-bans-156-combination-medicines-used-for-fever-pain-cold-6395411%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Thangalaan'%20box%20office%20coll