%20we%20do%20that%2C%20I%20believe%20we're%20going%20to%20be%20successful%20not%20only%20in%20winning%20this%20election%20but%20in%20saving%20the%20country%2C'%20Ramaswamy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamaswamy%20said%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20the%20right%20choice%20for%20the%20country%20and%20that%20he%20is%20doing%20everything%20he%20can%20to%20make%20sure%20he%20is%20elected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'We're%20only%20going%20to%20implement%20that%20agenda%20if%20we%20have%20control%20of%20the%20Senate%20and%20the%20House%20as%20well.%20So%20I'm%20doing%20everything%20I%20can%20to%20be%20helpful%2C%20while%20also%20continuing%20some%20of%20my%20own%20independent%20ventures%20in%20the%20business%20world%20now%20in%20the%20world%20of%20film%20and%20a%20couple%20of%20other%20areas%20where%20I%20think%20we%20could%20impact%20the%20country%20as%20well%2C'%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamaswamy%20is%20an%20executive%20producer%20of%20City%20of%20Dreams%2C%20a%20new%20movie.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20actually%20made%20by%20director%20who%20is%20an%20immigrant%20from%20India%2C%20Mohit%20Ramchandani.%20Very%20talented%20guy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20adding%20that%20the%20movie%20is%20coming%20out%20on%20August%2030%20%26quot%3BI've%20been%20involved%20in%20a%20number%20of%20my%20business%20ventures%2C%20have%20a%20book%20coming%20out%20called%20Truths%3A%20The%20Future%20of%20America%20First.%20That's%20come%20in%20in%20late%20September%20as%20well.%20So%2C%20a%20number%20of%20ventures%20outside%20of%20politics%2C%20because%20I%20think%20it's%20important%20to%20drive%20those%20changes%20in%20culture.%20But%20the%20most%20important%20objective%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20win%20not%20only%20the%20presidency%20but%20control%20of%20the%20House%20and%20Senate%20as%20well%2C'%20Ramaswamy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20entrepreneur-turned-politician%20slammed%20Harris%20for%20her%20open%20border%20policy.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20offensive%20to%20every%20legal%20immigrant%20to%20have%20an%20open%20a%20border%20to%20ten%20million%20people%20who%20enter%20this%20country%20illegally.%20I%20also%20think%20that%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20Indian-Americans%20do%20and%20should%20care%20about%20is%20merit%20in%20the%20country%20right%2C'%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20lot%20harder%20to%20get%20into%20a%20good%20college%20or%20even%20to%20get%20a%20job%20if%20you're%20have%20the%20wrong%20race%2C%20gender%2C%20or%20sexuality%2C%20but%20race.%20In%20the%20GOP%2C%20we%20want%20to%20end%20affirmative%20action%20not%20because%20we're%20against%20anybody%2C%20but%20because%20we%20stand%20from%20meritocracy.%20That's%20why%20many%20legal%20immigrants%20do%20come%20to%20this%20country.%20I%20think%20it's%20time%20we%20restore%20merit%20in%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724373300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Ffiva7t7_vivek-ramaswamy-_625x300_07_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-says-kamala-harris-is-cog-in-wheel-and-puppet-6397740%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20cog%20in%20the%20wheel%20and%20a%20puppet%26quot%3B%2C%20Republican%20leader%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20said%20on%20Thursday%2C%20and%20added%20that%20the%20Democratic%20presidential%20candidate%20is%20staying%20away%20from%20talking%20about%20policy%20in%20her%20speeches.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-says-kamala-harris-is-cog-in-wheel-and-puppet-6397740%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22DNC%20Day%204%3A%20Complet