20the%20people%20were%20probably%20under%2018%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20like%20it%20would%20be%20weird%20to%20try%20and%20interact%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20most%20importantly%2C%20it%20just%20didn't%20feel%20that%20fun%20for%20me%20to%20lovingly%20curate%20a%20profile.%20I%20used%20to%20love%20filling%20out%20a%20profile%20like%20this%2C%20showing%20off%20my%20impeccable%20taste%20and%20great%20jokes.%20Now%3F%20I'm%20tired.%20Maybe%20you%20just%20have%20to%20still%20be%2017%20to%20enjoy%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-instagram-stories-reels-made-comeback-beat-tiktok-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%20wants%20to%20appeal%20to%20Gen%20Z%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20it%20definitely%20does%20%E2%80%94%20then%20mining%20Myspace's%20greatest%20hits%20isn't%20exactly%20a%20bad%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram-music-profile-myspace-throwback-noplace-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724365246000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c7b89843b5e59d16b4874a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram-music-profile-myspace-throwback-noplace-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Now%2C%20you%20can%20add%20a%20song%20to%20your%20Instagram%20profile.%20Plus%2C%20there's%20a%20new%20popular%20app%20that's%20like%20an%20updated%20Myspace.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A270%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram-music-profile-myspace-throwback-noplace-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Husband%20of%20missing%20Northern%20Virginia%20woman%20arrested%20and%20charged%20with%20concealing%20a%20dead%20body%22%2C%22content%22%3