0female%20Vice%20President%20in%20American%20history.%20The%20seasoned%20lawyer%20will%20present%20her%20case%20in%20front%20of%20the%20delegates%20at%20United%20Center%20Arena%20in%20Chicago.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFrom%20Barack%20and%20Michelle%20Obama%20to%20Bill%20Clinton%2C%20senior%20figures%20have%20warned%20all%20week%20that%20Ms%20Harris%20has%20a%20brutal%20fight%20on%20her%20hands%20to%20beat%20the%2078-year-old%20Trump.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETim%20Walz%2C%20the%20Minnesota%20Governor%2C%20yesterday%2C%20accepted%20the%20Vice%20President%20nomination.%20He%20called%20it%20the%20%26quot%3Bhonour%20of%20his%20life%26quot%3B%20and%20shared%20his%20upbringing%20in%20a%20middle-class%20family%20in%20Nebraska%2C%20how%20he%20learned%20from%20helping%20his%20family%20on%20the%20farm%20and%20his%20experience%20of%20teaching%20students.%20These%20stories%20are%20intended%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20larger%20middle-class%20American%20population%20that%20is%20reeling%20through%20an%20economic%20slowdown%20coupled%20with%20inflation%20and%20unemployment.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMr%20Walz's%20son%2C%20Gus%2C%20stole%20the%20spotlight%20on%20day%203%20of%20the%20event.%20The%2017-year-old%20who%20is%20neurodivergent%20and%20has%20ADHD%2C%20was%20overcome%20with%20emotion%20as%20he%20watched%20his%20father%20take%20the%20stage.%20With%20tears%20streaming%20down%20his%20face%2C%20Gus%20stood%20up%20and%20proudly%20pointed%20at%20his%20dad%2C%20exclaiming%2C%20%26quot%3BThat's%20my%20dad!%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECelebrities%20like%20Oprah%20Winfrey%20endorsed%20the%20party's%20nominees.%20Ms%20Winfrey%20made%20a%20surprise%20entry%20yesterday%20and%20said%20%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20going%20to%20do%20is%20elect%20Kamala%20Harris%20as%20the%20next%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20And%20let%20us%20choose%20joy!%26quot%3B%20Winfrey%20said%2C%20a%20day%20after%20former%20president%20Barack%20Obama%20and%20his%20wife%20Michelle%20addressed%20the%20DNC.%26quot