aption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAmazon%20CEO%20Andy%20Jassy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D9e7ab9fadba6f83abce36abffe313d4a158b45dbb9b26206d3e1c41d842d10b8%26postID%3D66c756e07d61a86c18720874%26postSlug%3Damazon-ceo-says-ai-saved-crazy-amount-time-024-8%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.linkedin.com%252Fposts%252Fandy-jassy-8b1615_one-of-the-most-tedious-but-critical-tasks-activity-7232374162185461760-AdSz%252F%253Futm_source%253Dshare%2526utm_medium%253Dmember_ios%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20AI%20assistant%2C%20Amazon%20Q%2C%20drastically%20reduced%20software%20upgrade%20times.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJassy%20said%20that's%20saved%20the%20equivalent%20of%20thousands%20of%20years%20of%20work%2C%20plus%20millions%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20tools%20can%20enhance%20productivity%20across%20industries%2C%20including%20marketing%20and%20sales.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGenerative%20AI%20has%20some%20workers%20worried%20that%20it'll%20take%20their%20jobs.%20But%20before%20that%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20it's%20making%20some%20software%20engineering%20tasks%20a%20lot%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20CEO%20Andy%20Jassy%20revealed%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D9e7ab9fadba6f83abce36abffe313d4a158b45dbb9b26206d3e1c41d842d10b8%26postID%3D66c756e07d61a86c18720874%26postSlug%3Damazon-ceo-says-ai-saved-crazy-amount-time-024-8%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.linkedin.com%252Fposts%252Fandy-jassy-8b1615_one-of-the-most-tedious-but-critical-tasks-activity-7232374162185461760-AdSz%252F%253Futm_source%253Dshare%2526utm_medium%253Dmember_ios%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20August%2022%C2%A0that%20the%20company%20was%20able%20to%20integrate%20Amazon%20Q%2C%20its%20generative%20AI%20assistant%2C%20into%20its%20internal%20systems%C2%A0to%20update%20its%20foundational%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20has%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bgame%20changer%2C%26quot%3B%20Jassy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20average%20time%20to%20upgrade%20an%20application%20to%20Java%2017%20plummeted%20from%20what's%20typically%2050%20developer-days%20to%20just%20a%20few%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWe%20estimate%20this%20has%20saved%20us%20the%20equivalent%20of%204%2C500%20developer-years%20of%20work%20(yes%2C%20that%20number%20is%20crazy%20but%2C%20real).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20is%20not%20only%20fast%20but%20seems%20pretty%20accurate%2C%20too%2C%20according%20to%20his%20post.%20Amazon%20developers%20shipped%2079%25%20of%20the%20AI-generated%20code%20reviews%20without%20any%20additional%20changes%2C%20Jassy%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20benefits%20go%20beyond%20how%20much%20effort%20we've%20saved%20developers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20upgrades%20have%20enhanced%20security%20and%20reduced%20infrastructure%20costs%2C%20providing%20an%20estimated%20%24260M%20in%20annualized%20efficiency%20gains.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJassy's%20comments%20seem%20to%20tie%20into%20a%20often-used%20argument%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20AI%3A%20that%20it%20helps%20free%20up%20time%20otherwise%20used%20on%20boring%20but%20necessary%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20most%20tedious%20(but%20critical%20tasks)%20for%20software%20development%20teams%20is%20updating%20foundational%20software%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThis%20work%20is%20either%20dreaded%20or%20put%20off%20for%20more%20exciting%20work%E2%80%94or%20both.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20Amazon%20may%20be%20enjoying%20the%20increased%20productivity%2C%20developers%20might%20be%20concerned%20about%20its%20efficiency%20potentially%20reducing%20the%20need%20for%20human%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20Web%20Services'%20CEO%20Matt%20Garman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws-ceo-developers-stop-coding-ai-takes-over-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecently%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20internal%20meeting%20that%20software%20engineers%20may%20have%20to%20develop%20other%20skills%20with%20the%20proliferation%20of%20AI%20in%20coding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20go%20forward%2024%20months%20from%20now%2C%20or%20some%20amount%20of%20time%20%E2%80%94%20I%20can't%20exactly%20predict%20where%20it%20is%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20possible%20that%20most%20developers%20are%20not%20coding%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Garman%20is%20not%20the%20only%20top%20executive%20to%20express%20this%20warning.%20Nvidia's%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fi-wpzS9ZsCs%3Fsi%3D7G3H5xyeQYk14EYY%26t%3D2968%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Beveryone%20is%20a%20programmer%20now%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20AI%20coding%20tools.%20Emad%20Mostaque%2C%20Stability%20AI's%20former%20CEO%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FciX_iFGyS0M%3Fsi%3DV9_fWt2a8lgRqJb5%26t%3D825%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeven%20predicted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20there%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bno%20programmers%20in%20five%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDevelopers%20are%20not%20the%20only%20industry%20being%20hit%20with%20a%20potential%20extinction%20scare.%20Klarna's%20CEO%2C%20Sebastian%20Siemiatkowski%2C%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fklarna-ceo-comments-ai-smaller-marketing-team-produce-more-savings-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enow-deleted%20tweet%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20fintech%20firm%20will%20save%20%2410%20million%20this%20year%20by%20using%20generative%20AI%20to%20do%20the%20marketing%20work%20human%20employees%20previously%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20spending%20less%20on%20photographers%2C%20image%20banks%2C%20and%20marketing%20agencies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BOur%20in-house%20marketing%20team%20is%20HALF%20the%20size%20it%20was%20last%20year%20but%20is%20producing%20MORE!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Siemiatkowski%20received%20intense%20backlash%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.klarna.com%2Finternational%2Fpress%2Fai-helps-klarna-cut-marketing-agency-spend-by-25-and-run-more-campaigns%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20backed%20his%20enthusiasm%20for%20AI%2C%20saying%20that%20Klarna%20has%20%26quot%3Bgenerated%20over%201%2C000%20images%20in%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%202024%20using%20genAI%2C%20reducing%20the%20image%20development%20cycle%20from%206%20weeks%20to%20just%207%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Bank%20CMO%20Michael%20Lacorazza%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-saved-us-bank-months-of-development-time-on-a-new-brand-campaign-says-cmo-michael-lacorazza-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%3C%2Fa%3E%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company%20was%20able%20to%20use%20generative%20AI%20to%20%26quot%3Bshave%20about%20two%20and%20a%20half%20months%20off%26quot%3B%20their%20development%20cycle%20for%20a%20new%20brand%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20impressive%20efficiency%20increases%2C%20Lacorazza%20made%20it%20clear%20to%20reassure%20workers%20that%20he%20views%20generative%20AI%20as%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20replacement%20for%20humanity%20but%20an%20enabler%20for%20humanity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeantime%2C%20Jassy%20said%20that%20Amazon%20will%20continue%20using%20Amazon%20Q%20in%20further%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNot%20only%20do%20our%20Amazon%20teams%20plan%20to%20use%20this%20transformation%20capability%20more%2C%20but%20our%20Q%20team%20plans%20to%20add%20more%20transformations%20for%20developers%20to%20leverage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fww