's%20strategy%2C%20which%20makes%20a%20point%20I%20don't%20see%20in%20other%20Trump%2Fdudes%20discussions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20thing%20about%20dipshit%20outreach%20strategy%20is%20that%20while%20you%20can%20invent%20a%20kind%20of%20clever%20logic%20to%20support%20it%20%E2%80%94%20i.e.%2C%20the%20audience%20for%20Logan%20Paul%20and%20Adin%20Ross%20consists%20of%20guys%20who%20have%20some%20kind%20of%20natural%20affinity%20for%20Trump%2C%20but%20are%20also%20low-propensity%20voters%20(due%20to%20being%20dipshits)%2C%20and%20a%20consistent%20media%20campaign%20among%20them%20might%20increase%20turnout%20in%20the%20dipshit%20community%20%E2%80%94%20in%20practice%20a%20sizable%20majority%20of%20the%20dipshit%20audience%20is%2015-year-old%20boys%20who%20are%20not%20legally%20able%20to%20vote.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20teenage%20boys%20who%20aren't%20old%20enough%20to%20vote%20in%20your%20family%20(raises%20hand)%2C%20then%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20dipshits%20are%20enormously%20popular%20with%20teenage%20boys%20who%20aren't%20old%20enough%20to%20vote%20will%20not%20be%20news%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20as%20we%20keep%20pointing%20out%20here%2C%20the%20internet%20consumption%20habits%20of%20young%20people%20remain%20a%20mystery%20to%20lots%20of%20older%20people.%20Which%2C%20again%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-valuation-mrbeast-how-much-worth-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20reasons%20they%20don't%20understand%20why%20YouTube%20is%20so%20enormous%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20fair%2C%20the%20exact%20demographic%20breakdown%20of%20the%20dipshits'%20audience%20isn't%20readily%20available%2C%20in%20part%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram-youtube-advertising-teens-google-meta-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit's%20not%20in%20YouTube%20and%20other%20platforms'%20best%2