0large-scale%20joint%20military%20exercises%20around%20Taiwan%20with%20naval%20vessels%20and%20military%20aircraft%20in%20China%20on%20May%2024%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6658911acc442a2f676c2912%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221348%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20screen%20grab%20shows%20elements%20of%20the%20Chinese%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20during%20large-scale%20joint%20military%20exercises%20around%20Taiwan.%3Cp%3EGui%20Xinhua%2FPLA%2FChina%20Military%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20those%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20the%20most%20notable%20appeared%20to%20be%20that%20China%20%26quot%3Blaunched%20new%20efforts%20to%20erode%20Taiwan's%20control%20over%20its%20outlying%20islands%2C%26quot%3B%20switching%20from%20previously%20respecting%20Taiwan's%20%26quot%3Bde%20facto%20jurisdiction%20in%20waters%20around%20Kinmen%20and%20Matsu%26quot%3B%20to%20denying%20Taiwan's%20claim%20over%20those%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20exercises%2C%20China%20asserted%20%26quot%3Bits%20right%20to%20conduct%20law%20enforcement%20patrols%20in%20these%20waters%20at%20will%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said%2C%20noting%20a%20capsizing%20incident%20off%20Kinmen%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20developments%20involving%20the%20boarding%2C%20searching%2C%20and%20detaining%20of%20ships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKinmen%20and%20Matsu%20are%20two%20vulnerable%20islands%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20mainland%20China%2C%20sitting%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Xiamen%20and%20Fuzhou%2C%20respectively.%20Over%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20Chinese%20activities%2C%20particularly%20by%20the%20Coast%20Guard%2C%20around%20them%20have%20increased%2C%20notably%20spiking%20in%20May%20during%20Lai's%20inauguration%2Cas%20well%20as%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-showed-how-easily-no-notice-it-can-surround-taiwan-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_b