sway%20in%20the%20breeze%2C%20almost%20bowing%20down%20to%20him%20in%20thanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20passion%20project%20made%20of%20bamboo%20and%20wood%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20property%20around%20the%20Medini%20Homestay%20is%20filled%20with%20trees%20%E2%80%94%20glistening%20water%20droplets%20at%20the%20edges%20of%20the%20leaves%20refracting%20the%20light%20%E2%80%94%20almost%20featuring%20the%20entire%20forest%20in%20a%20single%20drop.%20The%20view%20from%20your%20room%20is%20glorious.%20A%20drone%20view%20of%20the%20property%20reveals%20two%20blocks%20of%20construction.%20As%20Meynell%20explains%2C%20these%20are%20the%20family%20block%20and%20the%20guest%20block.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20both%20identical%20and%20each%20has%20four%20rooms.%20The%20maximum%20capacity%20of%20the%20guest%20block%20is%20to%20accommodate%20nine%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-11-1724336150.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Medini%20Homestay%20is%20made%20out%20of%20bamboo%2C%20mud%2C%20wood%20and%20cow%20dung%20along%20with%20a%20small%20percent%20of%20concrete%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-11-1724336150.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-11-1724336150-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-11-1724336150-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-11-1724336150-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-11-1724336150-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20clas