ing%20to%20serious%20injuries%20and%20even%20becoming%20fatal.%20I%20experienced%20this%20firsthand%20when%20my%20grandfather%20passed%20away%20after%20a%20fall.%20Could%20we%20have%20prevented%20it%3F%20Perhaps%20not%2C%20but%20ever%20since%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20deeply%20troubled%20whenever%20I%20hear%20of%20someone%20over%2060%20or%2070%20taking%20a%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20teenagers%2C%20Rahi%20Shah%20and%20Hriday%20Boriawala%2C%20share%20similar%20worries.%20Rahi%E2%80%99s%20grandmother%20suffers%20from%20hip%20osteoporosis%2C%20and%20Hriday%E2%80%99s%20grandmother%20had%20a%20knee%20replacement%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337126%2Fmonitors-for-elderly-hemesh-chadalavada-invents-device-for-dementia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoth%20grandmothers%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20their%20age%20and%20health%20conditions%2C%20face%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20falling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Class%2012%20students%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20passionate%20about%20robotics%2C%20electronics%2C%20and%20coding%2C%20applied%20their%20knowledge%20to%20develop%20an%20innovative%20walking%20stick%20aimed%20at%20preventing%20falls%20%E2%80%94%20a%20common%20concern%20among%20the%20elderly%20and%20those%20with%20conditions%20like%20osteoporosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20kept%20brainstorming%20and%20found%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20to%20bring%20their%20solution%20to%20life%20during%20a%20STEM%20competition%20in%202022.%20They%20asked%20themselves%3A%20%E2%80%9CCould%20we%20create%20a%20preventative%20tool%20that%20would%20anticipate%20the%20risk%20of%20falls%20and%20alert%20caregivers%20in%20time%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20two%20years%2C%20the%2018-year-olds%20dedicated%20themselves%20to%20developing%20Walkfit%20%E2%80%94%20a%20system%20that%20attaches%20to%20a%20walking%20stick%20to%20assist%20with%20gait%20analysis%20and%20dia