%2Fuser-slams-indigo-airlines-for-cute-fee-company-responds%2Farticleshow%2F112644285.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20passenger%20on%20an%20Indigo%20Airlines%20flight%20asked%20about%20several%20charges%20on%20his%20ticket%2C%20notably%20the%20'Cute%20charge'.%20Indigo%20explained%20this%20fee%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Common%20User%20Terminal%20Equipment%20charge%2C%20covers%20amenities%20such%20as%20escalators%20and%20metal%20detectors%20at%20airports.%20The%20passenger's%20post%20received%20over%202%20million%20views%20on%20social%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fuser-slams-indigo-airlines-for-cute-fee-company-responds%2Farticleshow%2F112644285.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inspired%20By%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20Santiniketan%2C%20Bengal%20Man%20Starts%20%E2%80%98Tree%20School%E2%80%99%3B%20Innovates%20to%20Stop%20Dropouts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBiplab%2C%20a%20class%208%20student%20in%20the%20Bagdabra%20forest%20area%20in%20Murshidabad%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20is%20a%20first-generation%20learner.%20Studying%20in%20the%20government%20school%20nearby%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown%20was%20a%20big%20blow%20for%20young%20Biplab%20and%20his%20friends.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20tribal%20community%2C%20many%20students%20like%20Biplab%20started%20going%20to%20work%20with%20their%20parents%20as%20schools%20were%20shut.%20Access%20to%20online%20classes%20was%20a%20distant%20dream%20for%20these%20children%2C%20where%20basic%20resources%20remain%20out%20of%20reach.%20With%20no%20guidance%2C%20a%20hand-to-mouth%20existence%20forced%20these%20children%20to%20ultimately%20drop%20out%2C%20with%20schools%20remaining%20shut%20for%20almost%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tribal%20communities%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20the%20luxury%20of%20virtual%20lessons.%20Near%20their%20village%2C%20even%20before%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20regular%20tree%20plantation%20drives%20were%20being%20conducted.%20These%20expanses%20of%20green%20attracted%20the%20children%2C%20making%20them%20regular%20visitors%20at%20the%20site.%20As%20luck%20would%20have%20it%2C%20the%20person%20conducting%20these%20tree%20plantations%20was%20a%20teacher%20by%20the%20name%20of%20Angshuman%20Thakur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoticing%20the%20trend%20of%20school%20dropouts%20and%20seeing%20the%20children%20accompany%20their%20parents%20to%20work%20deeply%20moved%20the%2040-year-old.%20Since%20their%20schools%20provided%20mid-day%20meals%20to%20children%2C%20Angshuman%20first%20started%20providing%20the%20same%20to%20a%20group%20of%20five.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20meals%2C%20he%20also%20served%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330978%2Fkamlesh-atwal-started-nanakmatta-public-school-uttarakhand-holistic-education-for-students%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espoonfuls%20of%20knowledge%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethrough%20his%20open%20air%20classes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20alumna%20of%20Visva%20Bharati%20University%20in%20Santikentan%2C%20he%20imbibed%20the%20principles%20of%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20by%20providing%20a%20holistic%20education%20in%20sync%20with%20nature%2C%20which%20goes%20beyond%20merely%20words%20written%20in%20textbooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20with%20five%20children%20in%202021%2C%20today%20over%20105%20children%20study%20at%20Angshuman%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Anirvana%20Gacher%20Iskul%E2%80%99%20(Anirvana%20means%20inextinguishable%20and%20Gach%20means%20tree).%20Running%20on%20the%20benevolence%20of%20kind%20strangers%20and%20his%20own%20savings%2C%20it%20costs%20Rs%20300%20per%20month%20to%20educate%20a%20child%20in%20this%20school%20under%20a%20tree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELearning%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20nature%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAngshuman%20works%20as%20a%20Bengali%20literature%20professor%20at%20Prof%20Syed%20Nurul%20Hasan%20College%20in%20Farakka%2C%20Murshidabad.%20Raised%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20nature%20and%20inspired%20by%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20teachings%2C%20he%20pursued%20his%20higher%20studies%20at%20Visva%20Bharati%20university.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgacher-skul-min-1724074337.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20school%20is%20held%20in%20the%20open%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgacher-skul-min-1724074337.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgacher-skul-min-1724074337-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgacher-skul-min-1724074337-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgacher-skul-min-1724074337-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgacher-skul-min-1724074337-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361960%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20school%20is%20held%20in%20the%20open%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENature%20had%20always%20been%20his%20friend%20and%20supported%20him%20through%20thick%20and%20thin.%20While%20going%20through%20a%20tough%20time%20personally%20in%202019%2C%20the%20teacher%20sought%20solace%20in%20nature%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20noticed%20that%20the%20green%20cover%20was%20gradually%20reducing.%20I%20was%20depressed%20and%20wished%20to%20utilise%20my%20time%20in%20a%20productive%20manner%20post%20work.%20I%20put%20out%20a%20Facebook%20post%20in%202019%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20plant%20saplings%20and%20people%20were%20welcome%20to%20join%2C%E2%80%9D%20Angshuman%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20was%20overwhelmingly%20positive%20and%20led%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Gach%20Green%20Hands%20Social%20Welfare%20Trust%20whose%20first%20agenda%20was%20planting%2050%20saplings%20on%205%20June%202019.%20Being%20on%20the%20ground%20led%20to%20several%20interactions%20with%20locals%20and%20students.%20The%20teacher%20took%20some%20of%20them%20under%20his%20wings%20and%20would%20solve%20their%20doubts%20from%20time%20to%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20former%20students%20hailed%20from%20a%20village%20called%20Samlapur%20in%20Farakka%20and%20urged%20him%20to%20visit%20their%20village.%20It%20was%20after%20the%20first%20lockdown%20that%20the%20teacher%20visited%20the%20village%2C%20and%20he%20was%20astonished%20by%20what%20he%20saw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20setting%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F329929%2Farchana-nooguri-headmistress-government-school-national-teachers-award-enrollment-dropout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evillage%20matched%20Santiniketan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20beautiful%20and%20lush%20green.%20I%20had%20been%20meaning%20to%20start%20a%20school%20for%20children%2C%20and%20seeing%20the%20village%20and%20its%20children%20gave%20me%20the%20push%20I%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Angshuman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20financial%20backing%2C%20constructing%20four%20walls%20for%20a%20school%20was%20also%20not%20feasible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20tribal%20hamlet%2C%20Samlapur%20housed%20first%20generation%20learners%2C%20who%20were%20severely%20affected%20by%20schools%20shutting%20down.%20Their%20parents%2C%20who%20were%20daily%20wage%20workers%2C%20had%20no%20work%20and%20their%20worsening%20economic%20situations%20forced%20the%20children%20to%20go%20to%20work%2C%20dropping%20out%20of%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStudents%20were%20heavily%20dependent%20on%20the%20mid-day%20meals.%20The%20students%2C%20who%20hail%20from%20Adivasi%20families%20are%20extremely%20marginalised.%20I%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20continue%20their%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20Farakka%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20new%20age%20Santiniketan%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnirvana%20Gacher%20Iskul%2C%20an%20open%20air%20school%20under%20the%20shades%20of%20trees%20was%20born%20in%202021%20to%20provide%20an%20alternative%20school%20to%20these%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9jwkvXJXa7%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9jwkvXJXa7%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9jwkvXJXa7%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Gach%20Green%20Hands%20Social%20Welfare%20Trust%20(%40gachgreenhands)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20focus%20in%20the%20beginning%20was%20providing%20them%20basic%20education%20and%20meals.%20We%20started%20with%20five%20students%20and%20within%20a%20week%2C%20we%20had%20over%2020%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20Angshuman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20philosophy%2C%20the%20children%20are%20taught%20under%20neem%20trees%20and%20mango%20trees.%20A%20basic%20sense%20of%20environmental%20awareness%20and%20oneness%20with%20nature%20is%20inoculated.%20Concepts%20are%20taught%20by%20correlating%20them%20with%20what%20they%20see%20around%20them%2C%20instead%20of%20focusing%20on%20merely%20bookish%20knowledge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20from%20his%20own%20experiences%20as%20a%20student%20in%20Visva%20Bharathi%20university%2C%20the%20Anirvana%20school%20focuses%20on%20learning%20in%20sync%20with%20nature.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20studied%20in%20the%20open%2C%20under%20trees%20in%20Santiniketan%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20nature%20and%20culture.%20Unlike%20other%20colleges%2C%20where%20the%20focus%20is%20only%20on%20textbooks%20and%20curriculum%2C%20we%20are%20taught%20to%20be%20one%20with%20nature.%20Our%20creativity%20is%20enhanced%20and%20out%20of%20the%20box%20thinking%20is%20encouraged%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Anirvana%20school%20too%2C%20children%20are%20given%20an%20opportunity%20to%20learn%20drawing%2C%20artwork%2C%20dance%2C%20music%20and%20sports.%20Professional%20artists%20visit%20the%20school%20and%20teach%20the%20children%20simple%20clay%20modelling%20and%20other%20art%20forms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20these%20children%20are%20naturally%20very%20creative%20and%20very%20good%20at%20drawing%20and%20clay%20model%20making.%20We%20want%20them%20to%20explore%20their%20talent%20with%20locally%20available%20materials%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-52-min-1724074343.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20children%20are%20taught%20art%2C%20craft%20and%20culture%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-52-min-1724074343.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-52-min-1724074343-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-52-min-1724074343-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-52-min-1724074343-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-52-min-1724074343-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361962%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20children%20are%20taught%20art%2C%20craft%20and%20culture%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20schools%20reopened%2C%20the%20school%20continued%20to%20function%20before%20school%20hours.%20School%20starts%20at%206%3A30%20am%20and%20provides%20breakfast.%20They%20follow%20the%20government%20curriculum%2C%20but%20with%20a%20twist.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20teach%20them%20poems%2C%20stories%2C%20history%20from%20their%20syllabus%20with%20live%20examples%20found%20in%20nature.%20We%20help%20them%20relate%20whatever%20we%20teach%20with%20native%20examples.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20they%20are%20learning%20about%20flowers%2C%20we%20try%20to%20show%20them%20whatever%20followers%20are%20locally%20available%20which%20improves%20their%20understanding%20and%20leads%20to%20an%20appreciation%20of%20their%20surroundings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeachers%20are%20encouraged%20to%20teach%20this%20way%2C%20without%20poring%20over%20the%20books.%20Seeing%20the%20success%20of%20the%20school%2C%20the%20village%20%3Cem%3Emukhiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(head)%20gave%20them%20the%20community%20centre%2C%20where%20classes%20are%20conducted%20during%20the%20rainy%20season.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20ahead%2C%20Angshuman%20hopes%20to%20purchase%20some%20land%20and%20set%20up%20a%20school%20with%20an%20eco-friendly%20campus.%20He%20also%20wishes%20to%20set%20up%20a%20computer%20lab%20and%20library%20for%20the%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThrough%20this%20initiative%20and%20the%20children%2C%20we%20hope%20to%20improve%20the%20economy%20of%20the%20village.%20We%20are%20sowing%20the%20seeds%20of%20entrepreneurship%20in%20these%20children%2C%20which%20will%20reach%20the%20community%20and%20improve%20their%20livelihoods%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Angshuman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296463%2Fjharkhand-teacher-sapan-patralekh-teaches-parents-and-grandparents-improves-literacy-rate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eschool%20currently%20has%20105%20students%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20kindergarten%20to%20Class%2012%20and%20seven%20teachers.%20It%20costs%20Rs%20300%20per%20child%20per%20month%2C%20which%20is%20Rs%203%2C600%20per%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20support%20a%20child%20by%20donating%20through%20UPI%20on%207001714095%40axl%20or%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccount%20no%3A%2041165791703%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EName%3A%20Gach%20Green%20Hands%20Social%20Welfare%20Trust%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIFSC%3A%20SBIN0018784%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Angshuman%20Thakur%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724075548000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgacher-skul-min-1724074337.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D361924%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Moved%20by%20the%20plight%20of%20students%20displaced%20amidst%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20in%20Murshidabad%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Angshuman%20Thakur%20started%20the%20Anirvana%20Gacher%20Iskul%20in%202021.%20The%20open-air%20school%20focuses%20on%20practical%20learning%2C%20nature%2C%20culture%20and%20entrepreneurship%20for%20these%20first-generational%20learners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F361924%2Fopen-air-tree-school-west-bengal-murshidabad-inspired-by-tagore-santiniketan-anirvana-gacher-iskul-angshuman-thakur%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2269-YO%20Visually%20Impaired%20Man%E2%80%99s%20Old%20Age%20Home%20Helps%20Abandoned%20Seniors%20Find%20Friendship%20%26amp%3B%20Dignity%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20story%20is%20a%20very%20long%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%2069-year-old%20Laljibhai%20Prajapati%20warns%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20putting%20me%20off%2C%20this%20disclaimer%20has%20me%20intrigued.%20I%20am%20finally%20about%20to%20discover%20the%20journey%20of%20this%20visually%20impaired%20stalwart%20in%20starting%20a%20trust%20that%20has%20bettered%20the%20lives%20of%20over%20500%20senior%20citizens%20in%20the%20Kachchh%20region%20of%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20inception%2C%20Shri%20Navchetan%20Andhjan%20Mandal%20has%20been%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20disabled%20individuals%20in%20the%20state%2C%20particularly%20for%20abandoned%20visually%20impaired%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335260%2Fshantanu-naidu-startup-the-goodfellows-helps-senior-citizens-connect-with-youth-ratan-tata%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esenior%20citizens%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Left%20to%20fend%20for%20themselves%20by%20their%20families%2C%20these%20elderly%20individuals%20find%20comfort%20in%20Laljibhai%E2%80%99s%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20he%20takes%20great%20pride%20in%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20reveals%2C%20it%20all%20started%20when%20he%20was%2017%20years%20old.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20eyes%20were%20affected%20by%20glaucoma%20and%20I%20lost%20my%20vision.%20It%20was%20almost%20like%20I%20went%20to%20bed%20one%20night%20and%20woke%20up%20blind%20the%20next%20day.%20My%20life%20changed%20completely.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrapped%20in%20the%20four%20walls%20of%20his%20home%20with%20only%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20visits%20to%20look%20forward%20to%2C%20Laljibhai%20felt%20he%20was%20stuck%20in%20a%20proverbial%20tunnel%20%E2%80%94%20one%20without%20a%20light%20at%20the%20end.%20Losing%20his%20eyesight%20had%20done%20more%20than%20fluster%20him%3B%20it%20had%20also%20threatened%20to%20put%20a%20stopper%20on%20his%20career%20goals.%20He%20could%20no%20longer%20hope%20to%20study%20at%20the%20universities%20he%20was%20looking%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Bhachau%20(a%20city%20under%20the%20Kachchh%20district)%20native%20admits%20that%20no%20adversity%20could%20make%20education%20take%20a%20backseat.%20%E2%80%9CI%20began%20travelling%20around%20Gujarat%3B%20to%20Baroda%2C%20Jamnagar%20and%20Ahmedabad.%20I%20began%20studying%20at%20the%20colleges%20there%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F324715%2Fmeet-annie-worlds-first-self-learning-braille-device-that-also-acts-as-a-personal-tutor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20learning%20braille%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%20The%20reason%20to%20set%20his%20sights%20beyond%20Kachchh%2C%20he%20says%2C%20was%20because%20his%20home%20city%20did%20not%20cater%20to%20blind%20persons.%20In%20the%20years%20that%20followed%2C%20Laljibhai%20obtained%20his%20graduation%20degree%20in%20arts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20in%201975%20when%20h