20lacked%20toilet%20facilities%2C%20owing%20to%20its%20remote%20location%20and%20financial%20constraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20continued%20until%20architect%20Barnala%20Michael%2C%20architect-turned-documentary%20filmmaker%20Vishnupriya%2C%20and%20a%20group%20of%20like-minded%20friends%20came%20together%20to%20solve%20the%20social%20issue%20through%20collective%20effort%20and%20crowdfunding.%20Keeping%20the%20constraints%20in%20mind%2C%20they%20adopted%20an%20unconventional%20design%20approach%20with%20unique%20toilet%20units%20and%20cost-effective%20construction%20methods%20and%20techniques.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20they%20constructed%20three%20toilets%20and%20an%20open%20bath%20area%20that%20cost%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20%E2%80%94%20a%2030%20percent%20reduction%20in%20total%20cost%20compared%20to%20conventional%20construction%20methods.%20The%20technique%20allowed%20them%20to%20complete%20the%20project%20in%20just%20one%20month%20despite%20the%20limited%20financial%20and%20human%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20Michael%20to%20understand%20how%20they%20embarked%20on%20this%20mission%20to%20construct%20low-cost%2C%20sustainable%20toilets%20in%20the%20government%20school%20of%20Nellivasal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilet-1723867159.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vishnupriya%2C%20Barnala%20Michael%2C%20and%20a%20group%20of%20friends%20came%20together%20to%20solve%20the%20social%20issue%20through%20collective%20effort.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilet-1723867159.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilet-1723867159-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilet-1723867159-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilet-1723867159-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilet-1723867159-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361807%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVishnupriya%2C%20Barnala%20Michael%2C%20and%20a%20group%20of%20friends%20came%20together%20to%20solve%20the%20social%20issue%20through%20collective%20effort.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBy%20community%2C%20for%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20began%20when%20Vishnupriya%20came%20across%20a%20heartbreaking%20news%20report%20about%20a%20young%20girl%20who%20tragically%20lost%20her%20life%20due%20to%20health%20complications%20from%20constipation%2C%20caused%20by%20the%20absence%20of%20toilets%20in%20her%20school.%20This%20disturbing%20incident%20propelled%20her%20into%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20already%20been%20working%20on%20a%20documentary%20%E2%80%98Meel%E2%80%99%20to%20show%20solutions%20for%20waste%20management%20for%20the%20past%20seven%20years.%20So%20she%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20constructing%20low-cost%20eco-friendly%20toilets%20for%20the%20government%20school%20in%20Nellivasal%20village.%20After%20initial%20discussions%20with%20a%20group%20of%20like-minded%20people%20and%20friends%2C%20they%20approached%20Michael%20to%20devise%20a%20plan%20to%20solve%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20us%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20project%20come%20from%20areas%20of%20water%20scarcity.%20We%20have%20known%20the%20issues%20of%20toilet%20facilities%20and%20the%20pain%20of%20open%20defecation.%20This%20problem%20aggravates%20during%20the%20rainy%20season.%20This%20was%20a%20common%20emotional%20pain%20point%2C%20which%20motivated%20us%20to%20come%20together%20to%20solve%20this%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Michael.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20dire%20situation%20where%20children%20were%20forced%20to%20defecate%20in%20the%20open%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20proper%20facilities%2C%20struck%20a%20chord%20with%20Michael%20and%20led%20the%20team%20to%20focus%20their%20efforts%20on%20the%20government%20school%20in%20Nellivasal%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20why%20we%20chose%20to%20construct%20toilets%20in%20Nellivasal%20village%20was%20because%20of%20its%20difficult%20terrain%20where%20construction%20of%20toilets%20was%20challenging%20and%20school%20children%20were%20forced%20to%20defecate%20in%20the%20open.%20This%20could%20be%20a%20starting%20point%20and%20prove%20to%20be%20an%20example%20for%20other%20similar%20locations%2C%E2%80%9D%20Michael%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20team%20went%20to%20the%20government%20school%20in%20Nellivasal%2C%20they%20found%20a%20toilet%20was%20constructed%20on%20the%20premises%2C%20mainly%20used%20by%20the%20teachers%20and%20girls%20during%20school%20hours.%20However%2C%20Michael%20says%2C%20there%20was%20no%20toilet%20facility%20for%20hostellers.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20enquired%2C%20we%20got%20to%20know%20that%20the%20school%20had%20been%20trying%20to%20get%20funds%20for%20construction%20of%20toilets%20but%20they%20could%20not%20succeed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team%20constructed%20three%20toilets%20and%20an%20open%20bath%20area%20at%20the%20school%20campus.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361655%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20constructed%20three%20toilets%20and%20an%20open%20bath%20area%20at%20the%20school%20campus.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20sought%20permission%20from%20the%20forest%20department%20to%20construct%20low-cost%20and%20sustainable%20toilets%20for%20the%20school.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20given%20a%20month%E2%80%99s%20time.%20We%20found%20that%20mobilising%20construction%20materials%20and%20workers%20was%20difficult%20in%20the%20area.%20So%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20be%20smart%20in%20building%20toilets%20which%20will%20require%20less%20cost%2C%20time%2C%20and%20resources%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20project%20was%20entirely%20funded%20by%20volunteers%20of%20the%20Cuckoo%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20design%2C%20cost%2C%20technique%3A%20constructing%20unique%20toilets%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20preparing%20a%20rough%20design%20for%20toilets%20in%20October%202023%2C%20Michael%20and%20the%20team%20started%20constructing%20the%20toilets.%20They%20employed%20innovative%20construction%20techniques%2C%20opting%20for%20ferrocement%20structures%20to%20reduce%20costs%20and%20expedite%20the%20building%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFerrocement%20construction%20technique%20is%20a%20low-cost%20method%20that%20is%20less%20labour%20intensive.%20In%20this%2C%20reinforced%20cement%20is%20applied%20over%20a%20chicken%20metal%20mesh.%20Additionally%2C%20we%20used%20polycarbonate%20sheet%2C%20a%20translucent%20material%20that%20allows%20natural%20light%20and%20outside%20visibility%20that%20could%20enable%20students%20to%20feel%20slight%20resemblance%20with%20their%20old%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20also%20used%20a%20leech%20pit%20system%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F78181%2Fvideo-waterless-toilets-just-rural-india-needs%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DEco%2520sans%2520toilet%2520costs%2520about%2C%2527flush%2520out%2527%2520the%2520waste.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20management%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20turning%20human%20waste%20into%20natural%20manure%20for%20the%20school%E2%80%99s%20garden.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20system%2C%20two%20pits%20are%20connected%20to%20the%20toilet%20and%20they%20are%20built%20such%20that%20water%20gets%20drained%20through%20its%20walls%20and%20solid%20waste%20remains%20in%20the%20pit.%20When%20one%20pit%20gets%20filled%2C%20excreta%20is%20collected%20in%20the%20next%20pit.%20Meanwhile%2C%20solid%20waste%20in%20the%20former%20turns%20into%20manure%20in%20that%20period%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20construction%20of%20toilets%20has%20been%20extremely%20convenient%20for%20school%20children%2C%20especially%20hostellers.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20construction%20of%20toilets%20has%20been%20extremely%20convenient%20for%20school%20children%2C%20especially%20hostellers.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMichael%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWater%20is%20the%20main%20medium%20for%20the%20growth%20of%20microbes.%20When%20you%20remove%20water%20from%20solid%20waste%2C%20it%20does%20not%20cause%20any%20bad%20smell.%20Pits%20that%20have%20porous%20walls%20permit%20the%20contents%20to%20seep%20into%20the%20ground.%20Sawdust%20is%20applied%20to%20arrest%20the%20bad%20smell%20and%20microbial%20growth.%20It%20is%20a%20sustainable%20and%20natural%20way%20of%20waste%20management.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20Michael%20says%20they%20have%20designed%20the%20toilets%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20draws%20the%20interest%20of%20students%20who%20were%20accustomed%20to%20open%20defecation.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20built%20toilets%20in%20oval%20round%20shapes%20and%20adorned%20with%20vibrant%20colours%20to%20attract%20the%20students%20to%20use%20the%20enclosed%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F102470%2Fcarambolim-goa-village-eco-friendly-toilets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeco-friendly%20approach%20%3C%2Fa%3Enot%20only%20addressed%20hygiene%20concerns%20but%20also%20promoted%20sustainable%20practices%20within%20the%20community.%20The%20project%20was%20completed%20by%20November%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20their%20work%20was%20immediate%20and%20profound.%20The%20newly%20constructed%20toilets%20not%20only%20provided%20essential%20facilities%20but%20also%20triggered%20a%20behavioural%20change%20among%20the%20students.%20Built%20mainly%20for%20the%20boys%E2%80%99%20hostel%20at%20the%20campus%2C%20currently%20about%2080%20rural%20students%20including%20boys%20and%20girls%20are%20using%20these%20toilets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESriram%2C%20a%20Class%2012%20student%20of%20the%20school%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%20when%20there%20were%20no%20toilets%2C%20I%20would%20face%20a%20lot%20of%20problems%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20night.%20As%20it%20is%20a%20forest%20area%2C%20I%20feared%20going%20out%20for%20urination.%20These%20new%20toilets%20have%20brought%20immense%20comfort%20to%20us.%20I%20really%20like%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20toilets%20and%20also%20the%20paintings%20made%20on%20them!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Michael%20who%20visited%20the%20school%20a%20month%20back%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20the%20toilets%20were%20functioning%20properly.%20Now%2C%20there%20is%20no%20such%20issue%20of%20bad%20smell%20on%20campus%20and%20children%20are%20leading%20a%20regular%20school%20life.%20The%20improved%20sanitation%20conditions%20enhanced%20cleanliness%2C%20punctuality%2C%20and%20overall%20well-being%20of%20the%20school%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20hope%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F95712%2Fseva-mandir-rajasthan-ecosan-toilets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeco-toilets%20%3C%2Fa%3Espreads%20to%20schools%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20where%20students%20lack%20access%20to%20toilets.%20With%20our%20example%2C%20we%20hope%20to%20inspire%20architects%2C%20engineers%2C%20school%20teachers%2C%20and%20government%20officials%20to%20provide%20dignity%20to%20our%20students%2C%20protect%20the%20environment%2C%20and%20embrace%20sustainability%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5C